="https://www.newyorker.com/culture/the-new-yorker-interview/bon-iver-is-searching-for-the-truth" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约客》</em></a>个人资料中发表了评论，他问道：“我们为什么喜欢一首歌？是因为谁给我们唱歌吗？或者是这首歌？我只是觉得这首歌而已对我来说，确实如此。对我来说，重要的是歌曲和音乐的作用。” </p><figure id="attachment_3803674" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3803674" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3803674" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bon-iver-sable-review.jpeg" alt="邦伊弗黑貂评论" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bon-iver-sable-review.jpeg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bon-iver-sable-review-400x254.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bon-iver-sable-review-800x508.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bon-iver-sable-review-696x442.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bon-iver-sable-review-1392x884.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bon-iver-sable-review-1068x678.jpeg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3803674" class="wp-caption-text">邦·艾弗。图片来源：艾琳·施普林格</figcaption></figure><p><em>《NME》</em>给了《SABLE》<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/bon-iver-sable-ep-review-3803671">四星评价</a>，并指出：“但是，正如 2006 年搬回威斯康星州的年轻弗农所记得的那样，在与腺热和一段关系的结束作斗争时，邦·艾弗的根基存在于一种变化和不确定性。</p><p> “‘SABLE’可以提醒人们隧道尽头的曙光，也是克服逆境、迈向新篇章的理由。”</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-confirms-all-18-features-for-the-brat-remix-album-3799823">Vernon 出现</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>的“Brat”混音专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-and-its-completely-different-but-also-still-brat-review-a-masterpiece-in-the-art-of-club-music-curatorship-3802412">Brat And It&#39;s Completely Different But Also Still Brat</a> ”中，重新创作了歌曲“I think about it all the time”。</p><p>其他消息方面，今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-bon-iver-perform-at-kamala-harris-rally-in-wisconsin-3781912'">邦·艾弗 (Bon Iver) 进行了一场简短的表演，以支持卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 在威斯康星州举行的总统选举集会</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bon-iver-invites-fans-to-cover-his-songs-for-his-new-website-3808967">Bon Iver 邀请粉丝为他的新网站翻唱歌曲的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
