px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3763467" class="wp-caption-text">辛迪·劳珀。图片来源：Christopher Polk/Variety via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>不久之后，劳珀从座位上站起来，模仿自己使用助行器的样子，承认了自己的年龄。 “对我来说，我希望在我感觉强壮的时候有机会做到这一点。我想和人们一起庆祝。真正与人们一起庆祝，并让它变得有趣。”</p><p>在其他地方，这位古怪的偶像最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cyndi-lauper-proud-of-taylor-swifts-songwriting-3769794">分享了她认为泰勒·斯威夫特是多么“了不起”的歌曲作者。</a></p><p>在海莉·威廉姆斯的其他新闻中，她最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hayley-williams-says-paramore-have-been-working-on-new-music-3793718">透露帕拉莫尔正在创作新音乐</a>，并表示他们一直在玩的一个想法“感觉就像是在我们在家所做的音乐的另一边”。她补充道：“但这让我很兴奋。”</p><p>该乐队上次发行了 2023 年专辑《This Is Why》，<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/paramore-this-is-why-album-review-3393080">被<em>NME</em>评为四颗星</a>：“Paramore 终于达到了他们的音乐在过去十年中最好的阶段想要达到的目标。乐队并没有试图超越他们无与伦比的赞歌，而是在《This Is Why》中发现了一种新的温暖，效果确实是胜利的。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-hayley-williams-join-cyndi-lauper-to-perform-girls-just-wanna-have-fun-in-nashville-3808949">观看海莉·威廉姆斯 (Hayley Williams) 与辛迪·劳珀 (Cyndi Lauper) 在纳什维尔表演“Girls Just Wanna Have Fun”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
在壮观的伦敦 Troxy 演出中观看 The Cure 完整演奏《失落世界之歌》并庆祝《十七秒》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-troxy-london-songs-of-a-lost-world-seventeen-seconds-setlist-footage-photos-pedro-pascal-3808927?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-cure-troxy-london-songs-of-a-lost-world-7-secs-setlist-footage-photos-pedro-pascalAndrew Trendell Sat, 02 Nov 2024 10:34:04 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3808927 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE_CURE_TROXY_TOM_PALLANT_7.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="The Cure 于伦敦特罗克西 (Troxy) 现场演出。图片来源：汤姆·帕兰特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE_CURE_TROXY_TOM_PALLANT_7.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE_CURE_TROXY_TOM_PALLANT_7-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE_CURE_TROXY_TOM_PALLANT_7-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE_CURE_TROXY_TOM_PALLANT_7-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE_CURE_TROXY_TOM_PALLANT_7-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE_CURE_TROXY_TOM_PALLANT_7-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>随着佩德罗·帕斯卡 (Pedro Pascal) 和比莉·乔·阿姆斯特朗 (Billie Joe Armstrong) 等人在人群中翩翩起舞，The Cure 带着完整的新专辑和一系列热门歌曲进行了他们最后一场确认的演出。看看发生了什么并在此处重新观看节目</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-troxy-london-songs-of-a-lost-world-seventeen-seconds-setlist-footage-photos-pedro-pascal-3808927">观看 The Cure 完整演奏《失落世界之歌》并在壮观的伦敦 Troxy 演出中庆祝《十七秒》后，</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发布。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE_CURE_TROXY_TOM_PALLANT_7.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="The Cure 于伦敦特罗克西 (Troxy) 现场演出。图片来源：汤姆·帕兰特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE_CURE_TROXY_TOM_PALLANT_7.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE_CURE_TROXY_TOM_PALLANT_7-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE_CURE_TROXY_TOM_PALLANT_7-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE_CURE_TROXY_TOM_PALLANT_7-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE_CURE_TROXY_TOM_PALLANT_7-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE_CURE_TROXY_TOM_PALLANT_7-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/The-Cure">The Cure</a>昨晚（11 月 1 日星期五）在伦敦 The Troxy 举行的一场特别发布会上演奏了他们的新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-cure-songs-of-a-lost-world-review-lyrics-3801637">《Songs Of A Lost World》</a> ，并在那里庆祝了他们开创性的第二张专辑《Seventeen Seconds》问世 45 周年，同时还推出了一系列专辑。热门歌曲和最爱。请参阅下面的片段、照片和曲目列表。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-cure-songs-of-a-lost-world-review-lyrics-3801637">《治愈》——《失落世界之歌》评论：对失落的精彩反思</a></strong></li></ul><p>嘉宾名单中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">Green Day</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-joe-armstrong">Billie Joe Armstrong</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/RADIOHEAD">Radiohead</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ed-o-brien">Ed O&#39;Brien</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boy-george">Boy George</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mogwai">Mogwai</a>的 Stuart Braithwaite、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/DURAN-DURAN">Duran Duran</a>成员、演员 Mathew Horne 和喜剧演员 Stewart Lee、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pale-waves">Pale Waves</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/just-mustard">Just Mustard</a> 、Brian Cox 博士、Chris Packham、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/MY-BLOODY-VALENTINE">My Bloody Valentine</a>偶像 Kevin Shields 和即将走红的 Pedro Pascal，乐队继续庆祝他们 16 年来第一张专辑的发行，举办了一场售空的亲密演出在东伦敦。</p><p>继本周早些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-smith">Robert Smith</a>及其同事<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-bbc-radio-theatre-london-setlist-photos-watch-3808336">在 BBC 广播剧院为 Radio 2 和 6 Music 录制并播放了两场演出</a>后，昨晚的 Troxy 演出在 YouTube 上进行了直播，完整捕捉到了 Pascal 的精彩表演。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DB2NbZfv9gt/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.